2026-05-22T05:08:56.7774350Z 13    <!--
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7774977Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7792262Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7793538Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7794413Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7795415Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
