2026-05-22T05:08:56.7800652Z 22    <!--
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7801253Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7816475Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7817248Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7818240Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7819145Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7820063Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7820975Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7822090Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7822968Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7823798Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7824441Z 33    -->
2026-05-22T05:08:56.7825117Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
