2026-05-22T05:08:56.8937001Z 245        <!--
2026-05-22T05:08:56.8937674Z 246            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-22T05:08:56.8961766Z 247            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-22T05:08:56.8962843Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-22T05:08:56.8963818Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-22T05:08:56.8964652Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-22T05:08:56.8965521Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-22T05:08:56.8966543Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-22T05:08:56.8967505Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
