2026-05-22T05:08:58.4224535Z 272            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-22T05:08:58.4224911Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-22T05:08:58.4225284Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-22T05:08:58.4225746Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-22T05:08:58.4226172Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-22T05:08:58.4226542Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-22T05:08:58.4226897Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-22T05:08:58.4227246Z 279            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-22T05:08:58.4227475Z 280            preserve via tools:node="merge".
